These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, brown, grey, mauve, white
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bongani, montecristo, cain, fonseca
 1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the montecristo-smoker##5
 2. the person who likes black is the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is the person who likes black##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the fonseca-smoker##5
 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the person who likes white is not to the right of the cain-smoker##8
 7. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
 8. the person who likes white is not the montecristo-smoker##6
 9. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
10. the old-henry-smoker is not the person who likes mauve##6
11. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
13. the cain-smoker is not to the left of the montecristo-smoker##8
14. the person who likes grey is somewhere between the person who likes white and the montecristo-smoker##7
15. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Color        | brown | grey | white | mauve     | black    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | fonseca       | old-henry   | cain | bongani |

