.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, march, april, august, september
House: gothic-revival, wooden, palace, futuristic, victorian
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 2. the victorian house is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 4. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 6. the wooden house is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
10. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Birthday   | august | september    | december | march  | april |
| House   | gothic-revival  | futuristic | victorian      | wooden | palace |

