.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-3::.
There 5 different types of food: cherry, peas, peach, banana, potato
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, swisher, ritmeester, aristoff, game
1. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the game-smoker##8
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
3. the person eating peas is between the aristoff-smoker and the person eating banana##2
4. the person eating peas is the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the person eating potato is in the middle##1
6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person eating potato##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| Food           | banana | peas | potato | cherry | peach  |
| Cigar   | swisher  | ritmeester        | aristoff          | game     | dunhill |

