.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-4::.
City: colone, venice, berlin, prague, san-francisco
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, helicopter, train, snowmobile, quad-bike
 1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the taxi##7
 2. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
 3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
 4. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is not the person traveling to berlin##6
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 9. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to colone##7
10. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person traveling to venice##8
11. the person traveling to prague is the person traveling to prague##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is not the person traveling to prague##6
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
14. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| City   | berlin | san-francisco | prague | colone | venice |
| Transport           | taxi    | helicopter | quad-bike    | snowmobile      | train      |

