.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, handball, sailing, ice-hockey
House: cape-cod, palace, cottage, farmhouse, tower
 1. the farmhouse house is not to the left of the tower house##8
 2. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the cottage house and the farmhouse house##2
 4. the tower house is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the palace house is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
 7. the palace house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 8. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |    3    |   4   |    5    |
| Sport      | snowboarding   | soccer  | handball    | ice-hockey | sailing |
| House   | cape-cod | tower | farmhouse | palace | cottage   |

