 5. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
 6. the person eating orange is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
 8. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
