.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-15::.
5 different games are played: billiard, poker, chess, domino, bridge
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, cherry, blueberry, lemon, banana
 1. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person eating cabbage##8
 4. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 5. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 6. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
 7. the person eating blueberry is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 8. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
 9. the person eating banana is the person playing poker##1
10. the person playing bridge is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
11. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
12. the person playing chess is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating lemon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |  3  |  4   |      5      |
| Game      | domino | poker | bridge | chess | billiard |
| Food   | blueberry     | banana         | lemon | cherry | cabbage     |

