.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-20::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, july, december, october, august
5 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, guinea-pig, rat, chinchilla
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 3. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the owner of the cat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Birthday   | january  | august   | july | october    | december       |
| Pet         | cat | guinea-pig | rat     | hamster | chinchilla |

 